// Help Fragment In the home screen you have the option to enter appointments. If you have entered an appointment, the calendar icon at the bottom right will be animated, so you can immediately see that you have entered appointments. If you click on the icon, all appointments will be displayed immediately. Or you can click on the individual days where you will always be shown explicitly whether you have appointments for that particular day.

You can use the plus button that floats in the bottom middle to write a quick note. You can view and edit these in “Notes” -> (accessible via the bottom navigation). Furthermore, each quick note is also given the name Fast Note and has its own color.
// Help Text (Meditation) Focus on your breath and notice the sensations it creates as you breathe in and out. Feel the movement your stomach and your chest. Notice how the air flows through your nose and mouth. Take time to eat and enjoy it consciously. Pay attention to the colors, shapes and textures of the food. Notice the scent and taste every bite carefully. Integrate mindfulness into your everyday life by paying attention to simple activities such as brushing your teeth and washing up or driving a car. Be consciously aware of the processes and feel the sensations that arise.
